DrillBit didn't expect a quick response, and let the hoo punch strike
his jaw. He kept his attension on the bot, but lookewd at KitKat, out of
the corner of his eye.
"Oh, to hell with this. We are Predicons. SLAG HIM!!!" He yelled,
turning his right arm in to its gattaling gun form, and opened fire.
